msg: Transferred from the Adobe Open Source Subversion Repository

Added localizations of the 13 .properties files in modules/compiler for 13 new locales: Danish, German, Spanish, Finnish, French, Italian, Korean, Norwegian, Dutch, Portuguese, Swedish, Traditional Chinese, and Simplified Chinese. These files were provided by the LCDS team.
The Ant script for modules/compiler does not yet build locale JARs from these files.
Transferred from the Adobe Open Source Subversion Repository
Remove ADOBE SYSTEMS license, if present, and insert Apache license - modules.  Will need another pass to convert files not handled by the scripts.
